functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: Who are the protagonists of the top five Studio Ghibli movies with the highest Rotten Tomatoes ratings?
Who are the protagonists of the top five Studio Ghibli movies with the highest Rotten Tomatoes ratings?

The Studio Ghibli movies with the highest Rotten Tomatoes ratings are:

1. Spirited Away (2001) - Chihiro Ogino
2. My Neighbor Totoro (1988) - Satsuki and Mei Kusakabe
3. Kiki's Delivery Service (1989) - Kiki
4. Howl's Moving Castle (2004) - Sophie Hatter
5. Princess Mononoke (1997) - San and Ashitaka
